      "widgets_values": [
        "## Pixal3D Image \u2192 Textured 3D\n\nTencentARC **Pixal3D** single-image \u2192 textured mesh.\n\n- **Preprocess** \u2014 FOV estimate + background removal \u2192 pixal3d_input\n- **Image\u21923D** \u2014 `pipeline_type=1024_cascade` generates the **mesh + coloured voxelgrid** (shape + texture passes)\n- **CuMesh Simplify** \u2014 GPU decimate to a clean ~50k-face mesh\n- **OVoxel Texture Bake** \u2014 bake the voxelgrid colour onto the simplified mesh \u2192 **diffuse / normal / metallic / roughness** PBR maps + UV'd mesh\n- **Preview 3D** (textured) + **Export .glb** + save diffuse/normal\n\nNeeds the Pixal3D model at `TencentARC/Pixal3D` (auto-downloads on first run). GPU + a few minutes per run."
      ],
      "title": "\u2139\ufe0f About \u2014 \ud83e\udde0 BrainDead Pixal3D Textured"
    }
